    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the wacky world of the undead!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the late Mr. Stretch on his supernatural quest to reclaim his stolen fortune! The vengeful spirit of Mr. Stretch will stop at nothing to reclaim his treasures so that he can return them to his tomb and rest in peace. All that the ghost of Mr. Stretch remembers is that he'll do anything to get his fortune back.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stretch from wall to wall with Mr. Stretches unique movement style!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wind around spikes, change anchor points, and stretch into all sorts of crazy shapes to collect all of the gems that have been stolen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/48341c0563501d6a119ded5814036c5f.poster.avif?t=1730138869\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/48341c0563501d6a119ded5814036c5f.webm?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/48341c0563501d6a119ded5814036c5f.mp4?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore 40 levels of the spooky, dilapidated Stretch Manor...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront perplexing obstacles, and loot two unique areas of the manor with 3 more on their way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/b81b2d0977e09ee19a5b0525dd1d0038.poster.avif?t=1730138869\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/b81b2d0977e09ee19a5b0525dd1d0038.webm?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/b81b2d0977e09ee19a5b0525dd1d0038.mp4?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perfect Gem collection order to achieve incredible scores!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove yourself worthy of the ultimate treasure by getting good scores on all of the levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/80222bb4f04232a89b6b76047dc8df7a.poster.avif?t=1730138869\" width=768 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/80222bb4f04232a89b6b76047dc8df7a.webm?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/80222bb4f04232a89b6b76047dc8df7a.mp4?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge deadly ghost bosses and collect the treasure that is rightfully yours!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/67e514e004a81573dfc52e728f334679.poster.avif?t=1730138869\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/67e514e004a81573dfc52e728f334679.webm?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258130/extras/67e514e004a81573dfc52e728f334679.mp4?t=1730138869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Release:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >v0.2.0 &quot;Ghost In the Plumbing&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grand Entry and Waterworks Areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >42 Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Water, Pipes, Bubble Wands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legion Boss Fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Goji Boss fight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Next Major Update:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Green Thumb&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conservatory Area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21 Conservatory levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gem flowers, Plants/mushroom blocks, Chain Totems, 3 New Ghosts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gaia Boss fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Release: Story Elements (Cutscenes, Dialog)  Over 120 levels,  6 unique areas,  6 secret sub-areas,  7 bosses,  And over 70 Collectable journal pages.</p>",
